    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You whisper words of attraction, as a creature within range becomes infatuated by you. Choose one creature you can see within range, it must make a wisdom saving throw:</p><ul><li><strong>Success</strong>: No effect.</li><li><strong>Failure</strong>: The target gains a rank of charmed against you and must spend all its movement trying to get closer to you for the duration. an affected creature repeat their saving throw at the end of each of their turns, ending this genjutsu on itself on a success.</li><li><strong>Critical Failure</strong>: As a failure, but the creature treats you as an ally for the duration.</li></ul><p><strong>At higher ranks:</strong> For each rank above D-rank, increase this jutsu's cost by 3, and the number of affected creatures by +1.</p>",
